Show fleet nodes, service assignments, and service health

Usage: sleet status [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --addr <ADDR>
          Status endpoint of a sleet node (`fleet.http_addr`)
          
          [default: 127.0.0.1:7533]

      --format <FORMAT>
          Output format

          Possible values:
          - text: Human-readable text
          - json: JSON matching the subcommand's response schema
          
          [default: text]

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
